sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as HTTP Client
    participant App as FastAPI app<br/>main.py
    participant Schema as TransactionCreate<br/>schemas/transaction.py
    participant Route as create_transaction<br/>routes/transactions.py
    participant Service as TransactionService<br/>services/transaction_service.py
    participant Model as Transaction<br/>models/transaction.py
    participant Store as _transactions list<br/>in-memory

    Client->>App: POST /transactions JSON body
    App->>Schema: Pydantic parse and validate
    alt validation fails
        Schema-->>App: RequestValidationError
        App-->>Client: HTTP 422 JSON detail
    else validation succeeds
        Schema-->>Route: TransactionCreate
        Route->>Service: create_transaction(payload)
        Service->>Model: Transaction(id uuid4 type amount description created_at)
        Model-->>Service: Transaction instance
        Service->>Store: append(transaction)
        Store-->>Service: stored
        Service-->>Route: Transaction
        Route->>Route: TransactionResponse.model_validate(transaction)
        Route-->>App: TransactionResponse
        App-->>Client: HTTP 201 JSON TransactionResponse
    end
